g ( but that was a comedy ) . Oh , and Danny Boyle , but they were a different style of Zombie . Maybe Mr. Romero has ruined any zombie film for me due to his ingenious ability to get his actors to moan , groan and shamble about as if their joints are dried up and lacking even a drop of synovial fluid , and their muscles are fighting the effects caused by rigor mortis that had started to set in right before they were re-animated . The people of " " Wheelsy " " just didn 't have the proper motivation ... they were horrible zombies.So in the end I give " " Slither " " a 3 , for a couple of laughs and a few nice gore scenes . , " negative , , , , , , , , , , , ,
