reakthrough for her role of May , as she was previously best well known for her various role on TV series . As she do not have much movies in her career resume , The Mother has put her on the critic 's attention . Daniel Craig , on the other hand , had took on a similar role in his movie career , such as Sylvia ( 2003 ) and Enduring Love ( 2004 ) . If his reprising role of James Bond fails , film reviewers should not forget that he has a better performance in small productions in his years of movie career , and The Mother is one of them.The Mother may not be everyone 's favorite , but it is definitely not your usual matin챕e show to go along with tea and scones , accompanied by butter and jam . , " positive , , , , , , , , , , , ,
