ngs of the four protagonists , which occasionally results in redundant and tedious sub plots , but his reasons for this all become clear in the gruesome climax when the book suddenly turns out to be some type of Wishmaster-device . " " Mal챕fique " " is a dark film , with truckloads of claustrophobic tension and several twisted details about human behavior . Watch it before some wealthy American production company decides to remake it with four handsome teenage actors in the unconvincing roles of hardcore criminals . , " positive , , , , , , , , , , , ,
