e time it does in fact cast it 's uniquely original spell over you in spite of everything ; and unlike most platonic human and animal relationship stories it need not require a talking pig , monkey or shaggy dog to keep your interest throughout . ( * * * * * out of * * * * * ) , " positive , , , , , , , , , , , ,
