nd I can 't get enough . Watch it with an open mind , and just put your brain into neutral and enjoy ! ps -- don 't watch series 2 or later. series 1 was brilliant , the first few episodes of series 2 were good , but don 't watch it once it gets to Love and Monsters . Utter rubbish , completely destroys the show . , " positive , , , , , , , , , , , ,
